{"tid":442880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"橫 瀾 島 海 面 懷 疑 出 現 海 盜 1 人 受 傷","createTime":"2017-10-21T05:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T07:25:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7262a5a8213747a09d9391f46122a287e0c41037","tid":442880,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"橫瀾島海面懷疑出現海盜！上午11時15分，一名女子報警稱，收到其父親的電話求助，指一艘30米長的蝦艇在橫瀾島海面，被另外3艘船截停，有人持刀上蝦艇行劫。蝦艇上有13人，事件中1人受傷。警方正前往現場了解。"},{"pid":"e83320a7a3f80b4f9939f281547609480a730a9b","tid":442880,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"【13:30】水警初步了解後，懷疑是船隻碰撞起爭執，並非有人行劫。<br />\n<br />\n【12:30】警方找到據報的船隻，現正在場了解中。"},{"pid":"f6c775a5e77ef9d9d007f56e4958b6ab67b9dbfd","tid":442880,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.sysapi.news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/151059_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.sysapi.news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F151059_2.jpg&h=8b0c037c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"faab1ec3055e0217def1e773834670a8ac84ce27","tid":442880,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"香港連做賊都弱雞過人"},{"pid":"3547db06e2bde6c263ee19ee1cb2168c3a656669","tid":442880,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"香港都有海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf509dd7a37d4d708eb1c38857f99015b3a7f15","tid":442880,"uid":72058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T06:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港都有海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n張保仔"},{"pid":"363268ccfcc8b4fc024862e4777224bbb4b0957d","tid":442880,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T07:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset